 paparan mengenai arah kebijakan pembangunan Kota Bekasi, dengan menekankan sinergi antara perencanaan, penganggaran, pelaksanaan, dan pengawasan dalam pembangunan daerah.\n\n@sardiefendi78","post_time":1739361499,"owner":"71456575353","username":"dprd_kota_bekasi_komisi_2","comment_count":0,"like_count":40,"cdn_image":"//cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/pemkotbekasi/photo_gallery/picture/71456575353/DF-M5TSyzsf.jpg"},{"id":"DF4ydxzSwEg","image":"https://scontent-iad3-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.2885-15/476673834_18299692252230422_4606738847459963993_n.webp?stp=dst-webp_p720x720&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6IkZFRUQuaW1hZ2VfdXJsZ2VuLjEwODB4MTM1MC5zZHIuZjc1NzYxLmRlZmF1bHRfaW1hZ2UifQ&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=102&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2QHboJlwslSTWyBqfS5rnzcUzIa5JKKWAbsoAXYUvynVXVal-gM2uD8BJn1HzRAjgUg&_nc_ohc=3iK0_UQEJ8kQ7kNvwFXflti&_nc_gid=TYr1Vs5fnVWGXjNLuRDnsA&edm=APoiHPcBAAAA&ccb=7-5&ig_cache_key=MzU2NDgyMTA1MzcyODAzMTAwOA%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&oh=00_AfP7cGE33NaCrVbcTfWNwUJxW8lfnOvzzEbHkX9RdBl5pg&oe=685FA304&_nc_sid=22de04","caption":"Selamat Hari Pers Nasional 9 Februari 2025","post_time":1739179806,"owner":"71456575353","username":"dprd_kota_bekasi_komisi_2","comment_count":0,"like_count":30,"cdn_image":"//cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/pemkotbekasi/photo_gallery/picture/71456575353/DF4ydxzSwEg.jpg"},{"id":"DFWf5kTSP1_","image":"https://scontent-iad3-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.2885-15/475528813_18298200199230422_3327921037571426053_n.webp?stp=dst-webp_s720x720&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6IkZFRUQuaW1hZ2VfdXJsZ2VuLjEwODB4MTA4MC5zZHIuZjc1NzYxLmRlZmF1bHRfaW1hZ2UifQ&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=102&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2QHboJlwslSTWyBqfS5rnzcUzIa5JKKWAbsoAXYUvynVXVal-gM2uD8BJn1HzRAjgUg&_nc_ohc=VFCu_KHvaA4Q7kNvwHfj_bL&_nc_gid=TYr1Vs5fnVWGXjNLuRDnsA&edm=APoiHPcBAAAA&ccb=7-5&ig_cache_key=MzU1NTE2OTI1MTI4NTg1OTcxMQ%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&oh=00_AfMoDWmaFk6tt5BDCdBe0NEI6RtEjhPOUUxk_4oG25I8kA&oe=685F9B7E&_nc_sid=22de04","caption":"Pimpinan & Anggota DPRD Kota Bekasi mengucapkan selamat memperingati Isra Mi'